&quot; data-entity-uuid=&quot;5f56c281-a834-47e7-8681-7806f7bb2aff&quot; src=&quot;/sites/default/files/inline-images/Black%20woman%20hugging%20her%20mother%20as%20she%20sits%20inside%20of%20a%20house%20indoors%20at%20home%20copy.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;  &lt;div class=&quot;col-md-6 col-md-pull-6&quot;&gt; &lt;p&gt;Finding the right information about disabilities can be challenging, overwhelming, and can sometimes seem impossible.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;The Ability Central Portal is here to make it easy to find relevant, researched information about a disability created by and for Deaf, disabled, and neurodiverse communities.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;              &lt;div class=&quot;container-fluid&quot;&gt;         &lt;div class=&quot;row homepage-v3-portal-features&quot;&gt;           &lt;div class=&quot;container&quot;&gt;             &lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;                              &lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field--item&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-12 clearfix text-highlight&quot;&gt; &lt;h2 class=&quot;text-center&quot;&gt;What can I do on the Portal?&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p class=&quot;text-center&quot;&gt;Ability Central is your Portal to a more accessible world for all.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3 feature&quot;&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/devices/library/&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fa icon-fax feature-icon&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Discover&lt;/strong&gt; phones and tablets that fit your unique needs.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3 feature&quot;&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/services/&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fa icon-map-marker feature-icon&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Locate&lt;/strong&gt; support services for people with disabilities.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3 feature&quot;&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/articles/library/&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fa icon-newspapper-o feature-icon&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Find&lt;/strong&gt; and share disability-related news and resources.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3 feature&quot;&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/events/list/&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fa icon-event feature-icon&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Connect&lt;/strong&gt; with local members of your community.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;                    &lt;/div&gt;           &lt;/div&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;                    &lt;div class=&quot;container pt-6&quot;&gt;         &lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;           &lt;div class=&quot;col-xs-12 pb-4&quot;&gt;             &lt;h2&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fa icon-newspapper-o feature-icon&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Recent articles&lt;/h2&gt;           &lt;/div&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;div class=&quot;views-element-container form-group&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;container view view-recent-articles view-id-recent_articles view-display-id-ccaf js-view-dom-id-038622f939a62c447eb4059e71ca81c044f28c90332e392ca79b71d9d0cd94ac&quot;&gt;                      &lt;div class=&quot;view-content&quot;&gt;              &lt;div class=&quot;row equal&quot;&gt;                               &lt;div class=&quot;col-xs-12 col-md-4 pb-6&quot;&gt;           &lt;div class=&quot;homepage-v3-article&quot;&gt;             &lt;img src=&quot;/sites/default/files/2022-08/Self-Determination%20featured%20image%204.png&quot; width=&quot;1200&quot; height=&quot;800&quot; alt=&quot;graphic showing the title of the article: &amp;quot;Self-Determination Program and the Financial Management Services Provider&amp;quot; on a green background&quot; class=&quot;img-responsive&quot;&gt;             &lt;h4 class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Self-Determination Program and the Financial Management Services Provider&lt;/h4&gt;             &lt;div class=&quot;content pb-2&quot;&gt;California’s Self-Determination Program (SDP) provides disabled individuals the opportunity to take agency and control over the services offered by implementing...&lt;/div&gt;             &lt;div class=&quot;button-wrapper text-center&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;btn-button-solid&quot; href=&quot;/article/self-determination-program-and-financial-management-services-provider&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Read more&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;           &lt;/div&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;                               &lt;div class=&quot;col-xs-12 col-md-4 pb-6&quot;&gt;           &lt;div class=&quot;homepage-v3-article&quot;&gt;             &lt;img src=&quot;/sites/default/files/2022-08/Self-Determination%20featured%20image%203.png&quot; width=&quot;1200&quot; height=&quot;800&quot; alt=&quot;graphic showing the title of the article: &amp;quot;Person-Centered Planning in the Self-Determination Program&amp;quot; on a green background&quot; class=&quot;img-responsive&quot;&gt;             &lt;h4 class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Person-Centered Planning in the Self-Determination Program&lt;/h4&gt;             &lt;div class=&quot;content pb-2&quot;&gt;The Self-Determination Program (SDP) is an alternative option facilitated by the regional centers for people with disabilities to choose personalized support an...&lt;/div&gt;             &lt;div class=&quot;button-wrapper text-center&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;btn-button-solid&quot; href=&quot;/article/person-centered-planning-self-determination-program&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Read more&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;           &lt;/div&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;                               &lt;div class=&quot;col-xs-12 col-md-4 pb-6&quot;&gt;           &lt;div class=&quot;homepage-v3-article&quot;&gt;             &lt;img src=&quot;/sites/default/files/2022-08/Self-Determination%20featured%20image%202.png&quot; width=&quot;1200&quot; height=&quot;800&quot; alt=&quot;graphic showing the title of the article: &amp;quot;The Growth of Self-Determination in California&amp;quot; on a green background&quot; class=&quot;img-responsive&quot;&gt;             &lt;h4 class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;The Growth of Self-Determination in California&lt;/h4&gt;             &lt;div class=&quot;content pb-2&quot;&gt;Born from the desire of disability advocates to implement a more person-centered approach, Self-Determination Programs (SDP) have prospered in the United States...&lt;/div&gt;             &lt;div class=&quot;button-wrapper text-center&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;btn-button-solid&quot; href=&quot;/article/growth-self-determination-california&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Read more&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;           &lt;/div&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;           &lt;/div&gt;        &lt;/div&gt;              &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;                     &lt;div class=&quot;container-fluid pt-6&quot;&gt;         &lt;div class=&quot;row homepage-v3-finder&quot;&gt;           &lt;div class=&quot;container&quot;&gt;             &lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;               &lt;div class=&quot;col-xs-12 col-sm-5 pb-6&quot;&gt; &lt;h2 class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fa icon-fax icon&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Find devices&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p class=&quot;body pt-2 pb-2&quot;&gt;Browse our international database of mobile phones and tablets to find the right device for you.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;button-wrapper text-center&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;btn-button-solid&quot; href=&quot;/devices/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Get started&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;col-xs-12 col-sm-2&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;col-xs-12 col-sm-5&quot;&gt; &lt;h2 class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fa icon-map-marker icon&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Find services&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p class=&quot;body pt-2 pb-2&quot;&gt;Search nationwide for organizations that provide support services for people with disabilities.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;button-wrapper text-center&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;btn-button-solid&quot; href=&quot;/services/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Get started&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;             &lt;/div&gt;           &lt;/div&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;                    &lt;div class=&quot;container pt-6&quot;&gt;         &lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;           &lt;div class=&quot;col-xs-12 pb-4&quot;&gt;             &lt;h2&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fa icon-event feature-icon&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Upcoming events&lt;/h2&gt;           &lt;/div&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;div class=&quot;views-element-container form-group&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;container pb-6 view view-upcoming-events view-id-upcoming_events view-display-id-ccaf_events js-view-dom-id-56a73bc637461dd24ade4b757eed95611c0b4d62b6ef1ff6c0fef05ee6ac425e&quot;&gt;                      &lt;div class=&quot;view-content&quot;&gt;             &lt;div class=&quot;row equal&quot;&gt;               &lt;div class=&quot;col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3 pb-2&quot;&gt;           &lt;div class=&quot;homepage-v3-upcoming-event&quot;&gt;                  &lt;h3 class=&quot;date&quot;&gt;&lt;time datetime=&quot;2022-11-29T20:30:00Z&quot;&gt;Nov 29&lt;/time&gt; &lt;/h3&gt;     &lt;p class=&quot;name&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/events/al-or-vis-low-vision-group-phone-call-zoom-25&quot; hreflang=&quot;en&quot;&gt;Al or VIS Low Vision Group by Phone Call in Zoom&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;            &lt;/div&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;               &lt;div class=&quot;col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3 pb-2&quot;&gt;           &lt;div class=&quot;homepage-v3-upcoming-event&quot;&gt;                  &lt;h3 class=&quot;date&quot;&gt;&lt;time datetime=&quot;2022-11-29T20:30:00Z&quot;&gt;Nov 29&lt;/time&gt; &lt;/h3&gt;     &lt;p class=&quot;name&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/events/low-vision-party-line-call-25&quot; hreflang=&quot;en&quot;&gt;Low Vision Party Line / Call-In&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;            &lt;/div&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;               &lt;div class=&quot;col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3 pb-2&quot;&gt;           &lt;div class=&quot;homepage-v3-upcoming-event&quot;&gt;                  &lt;h3 class=&quot;date&quot;&gt;&lt;time datetime=&quot;2022-11-29T14:30:00Z&quot;&gt;Nov 29&lt;/time&gt; &lt;/h3&gt;     &lt;p class=&quot;name&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/events/al-or-vis-low-vision-group-phone-call-zoom-25&quot; hreflang=&quot;en&quot;&gt;Al or VIS Low Vision Group by Phone Call in Zoom&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;            &lt;/div&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;             &lt;div class=&quot;col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3&quot; style=&quot;align-self: center;&quot;&gt;         &lt;div class=&quot;button-wrapper text-center&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;btn-button-solid&quot; href=&quot;/events/list/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Discover more&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;        &lt;/div&gt;              &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;                     &lt;div class=&quot;container&quot;&gt;         &lt;div class=&quot;row homepage-v3 pt-6 pb-6&quot;&gt;           &lt;div class=&quot;col-xs-12 clearfix pb-6&quot;&gt; &lt;h2&gt;We’re helping people help people.&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;col-xs-12 col-md-6 pb-4&quot;&gt; &lt;img alt=&quot;Young person with disability sits at a desk with a laptop smiling to two women, one standing and the other sitting.&quot; class=&quot;img-responsive&quot; src=&quot;/sites/default/files/2022-06/section-were-helping-people-help-people.jpg&quot;&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;col-xs-12 col-md-6&quot;&gt; &lt;p&gt;We’re Ability Central, a non-profit organization serving as an educator, convener, and resource for people with disabilities and their communities of support.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;We created the Portal because we are on a mission to transform the field of communications and information access so that all individuals can realize their right to receive information and express themselves.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;button-wrapper pt-2&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;btn-button-solid&quot; href=&quot;/about-ability-central-web-portal/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Learn more&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;      &lt;/div&gt;            &lt;/div&gt;   &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;div class=&quot;container pre-footer-v3 hidden-xs hidden-sm&quot;&gt;   &lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;     &lt;div class=&quot;col-md-12 attribute-menu&quot;&gt;       &lt;h4 class=&quot;title text-center&quot;&gt;Find information based on disability:&lt;/h4&gt;              &lt;ul class=&quot;menu menu--attribute nav&quot;&gt;                       &lt;li class=&quot;menu-icon menu-icon-13 first&quot;&gt;                                         &lt;a href=&quot;/resources/attributes/deaf&quot; data-drupal-link-system-path=&quot;taxonomy/term/7&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fa icon-deaf&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-text&quot;&gt;Deaf&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;               &lt;/li&gt;                       &lt;li class=&quot;menu-icon menu-icon-14&quot;&gt;                                         &lt;a href=&quot;/resources/attributes/hearing-loss&quot; data-drupal-link-system-path=&quot;taxonomy/term/9&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fa icon-assistive-listening-systems&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-text&quot;&gt;Hearing Loss&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;               &lt;/li&gt;                       &lt;li class=&quot;menu-icon menu-icon-15&quot;&gt;                                         &lt;a href=&quot;/resources/attributes/speech&q